I saw this in an e-mail;
On Fri, Mar 22, 2013 at 9:28 AM, Ken Edwards <ken.edwards@eucalyptus.com> wrote:
The root cause is a proxy bug. The single proxy is sending request too fast to the CLC (causing replay detection errors).

[~dkavanagh], I have been able to reproduce this issue by creating a tag on an instance and running:

{code}
  for X in {1..520}; do euca-describe-tags; done
{code}
